616
00:37:46.484 --> 00:37:49.424
No dose-limiting toxicities were observed.

617
00:37:49.984 --> 00:37:53.624
The maximum tolerated dose was not reached, and 1,200

618
00:37:53.664 --> 00:37:57.614
milligrams oral daily was selected as the recommended Phase

619
00:37:57.664 --> 00:38:01.644
2 dose in pancreatic adenocarcinoma and non-small cell lung

620
00:38:01.704 --> 00:38:05.564
cancer, including the part two of this study, expansion and dose

621
00:38:05.664 --> 00:38:06.564
